CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 4, 1958, pg. A1 reads: "Helping The City - High school students of the Manchester area begin their treks to homes of hundred of families on Monday to inform them of the city's urban renewal program which will displace all families in 164-acre Manchester section. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Manchester high school students, including young women in front wearing head scarves and eyeglasses, walking down steps of Manchester Community House, street no. 1522
